#: .\ammo.json
msgid "maid's blob feed"
msgid_plural "maid's blob feeds"
msgstr[0] "女僕的粘液飼料"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's blob feed"}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Feed made for a certain type of blob. It's a protein paste made out of meat."
msgstr "專為某種粘液生物製作的飼料。這是一種由肉類製成的蛋白質糊。"

#: .\ammo.json .\ammo_types.json
msgid "assassin's throwing knife"
msgid_plural "assassin's throwing knifes"
msgstr[0] "刺客的飛刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "assassin's throwing knife"}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"A nimble blade meant for ranged assassination, but makes an improvised "
"cutlery tool in a pinch. It's very lightweight and silent and can be used on"
" both zombies and games involving apples."
msgstr "為遠程暗殺設計的靈巧刀刃，緊急時也能充當臨時餐具。它非常輕巧且安靜，既可用於對付殭屍，也能參與涉及蘋果的遊戲。"

#: .\ammo.json .\ammo_types.json
msgid "makeshift throwing knife"
msgid_plural "makeshift throwing knifes"
msgstr[0] "臨時飛刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'makeshift throwing knife'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"A crude and simple throwing knife made from a sharpened piece of salvaged "
"steel with cloth wrapped around it. It's better than throwing rocks, at "
"least."
msgstr "用磨利的回收鋼材包裹布料製成的粗糙簡易飛刀。至少比扔石頭強些。"

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "maid's ladle"
msgid_plural "maid's ladles"
msgstr[0] "女僕的長柄勺"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': "maid's ladle"}.
#: .\ammo.json
msgid "You are overcome with anger."
msgstr "你被憤怒所淹沒。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's ladle"}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid "A weapon used by a maid when she's seriously angry. Scary!"
msgstr "女僕真正發怒時使用的武器。真嚇人！"

#. ~ Use action no_deactivate_msg for {'str': "maid's ladle"}.
#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's ladle"}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid "This is an outrage! You're on the verge of exploding!"
msgstr "這太離譜了！你快要氣炸了！"

#. ~ Use action sound_msg for {'str': "maid's ladle"}.
#: .\ammo.json
msgid "You are so furious that even the earth begins to rumble..."
msgstr "你怒不可遏，連大地都開始震顫……"

#: .\ammo.json
msgid "maid energy crystal"
msgid_plural "maid energy crystal"
msgstr[0] "女僕能量水晶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'maid energy crystal', 'str_pl': 'maid energy
#. crystal'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"A crystallized manifestation of passion. Acts as a source of energy in "
"certain types of tools for maids."
msgstr "激情結晶化的體現。作為某些女僕專用工具的能量來源。"

#: .\ammo.json .\ammo_types.json
msgid "Maid Power"
msgid_plural "Maid Power"
msgstr[0] "女僕之力"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Maid Power', 'str_pl': 'Maid Power'}
#: .\ammo.json
msgid ""
"A semi-crystallized manifestation of passion, not yet fully catalyzed into a"
" usable form."
msgstr "半結晶化的激情體現，尚未完全催化為可用形態。"

#: .\ammo_types.json
msgid "blob's breakfast"
msgstr "粘液的早餐"

#: .\ammo_types.json
msgid "Maid Point"
msgstr "女僕點數"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "Victorian maid dress"
msgid_plural "Victorian maid dresses"
msgstr[0] "維多利亞式女僕裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Victorian maid dress', 'str_pl': 'Victorian maid
#. dresses'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A classic maid outfit with a white apron, frills and a black one piece. It "
"has some storage space thanks to the apron and side pockets, including space"
" for throwing knives. Since it comes with bloomers, you can take off your "
"underwear and not feel embarrassed about it!"
msgstr ""
"經典女僕裝，配有白色圍裙、褶邊和黑色連身裙。得益於圍裙和側袋，它提供了一些儲物空間，包括存放飛刀的位置。由於自帶燈籠褲，你可以脫掉內衣而不會感到尷尬！"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "French maid dress"
msgid_plural "French maid dresses"
msgstr[0] "法式女僕裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'French maid dress', 'str_pl': 'French maid
#. dresses'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A French maid dress in the modern style, black with a frilly white apron. "
"Doesn't cover much past the thigh or shoulder."
msgstr "現代風格的法式女僕裝，黑色底色配褶邊白色圍裙。大腿或肩部以上覆蓋甚少。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "strange French maid dress"
msgid_plural "strange French maid dresses"
msgstr[0] "奇怪的法式女僕裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'strange French maid dress', 'str_pl': 'strange
#. French maid dresses'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A French maid dress in the modern style, black with a frilly white apron. "
"Doesn't cover much past the thigh or shoulder. Something seems off about it."
msgstr "現代風格的法式女僕裝，黑色底色配褶邊白色圍裙。大腿或肩部以上覆蓋甚少。但似乎有些不對勁。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "survivor Victorian maid dress"
msgid_plural "survivor Victorian maid dresses"
msgstr[0] "倖存者維多利亞女僕裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor Victorian maid dress', 'str_pl':
#. 'survivor Victorian maid dresses'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A Victorian maid dress tailored specifically for post-cataclysm maids. The "
"kevlar weave provides modest protection, but makes it somewhat harder to "
"move in."
msgstr "專為災後世界女僕量身定製的維多利亞式女僕裝。凱夫拉編織提供適度防護，但也使得行動略顯不便。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "Jokyu dress"
msgid_plural "Jokyu dresses"
msgstr[0] "女給服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Jokyu dress', 'str_pl': 'Jokyu dresses'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"Women's servant clothes worn in Japanese cafes a long time ago. Essentially "
"a white apron over a kimono."
msgstr "很久以前日本咖啡館中女性侍者穿著的服飾。本質上是在和服外罩一件白色圍裙。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "lace stockings with garterbelt"
msgid_plural "lace stockings with garterbelts"
msgstr[0] "蕾絲吊帶襪配束腰帶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lace stockings with garterbelt', 'str_pl': 'lace
#. stockings with garterbelts'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A set of pure white stockings with garterbelt and panties, decorated with "
"elegant lacing."
msgstr "一套純白色吊帶襪配束腰帶和內褲，飾有優雅的蕾絲花邊。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "tuxedo"
msgid_plural "tuxedos"
msgstr[0] "燕尾服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tuxedo'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid "A full-body tuxedo.  Makes the apocalypse feel a little more classy."
msgstr "一套全身燕尾服。讓末日世界也顯得更有格調。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "survivor tuxedo"
msgid_plural "survivor tuxedos"
msgstr[0] "倖存者燕尾服"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor tuxedo'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A tux tailored specifically for post-cataclysm butlers. The kevlar weave "
"provides modest protection, but makes it somewhat harder to move in."
msgstr "專為災後管家量身定製的燕尾服。凱夫拉編織提供適度的防護，但也使得行動略顯不便。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "maid cap"
msgid_plural "maid caps"
msgstr[0] "女僕帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'maid cap'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid "A frilly white cap commonly used by maids."
msgstr "女僕常用的帶褶邊白色帽子。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "strange maid headband"
msgid_plural "strange maid headbands"
msgstr[0] "怪異女僕頭帶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'strange maid headband'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A frilly white headband commonly used by maids. Something seems off about "
"it."
msgstr "女僕常用的帶褶邊白色頭帶。它似乎有些不對勁。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "cat eared maid cap"
msgid_plural "cat eared maid caps"
msgstr[0] "貓耳女僕帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cat eared maid cap'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A frilly white cap commonly used by maids. There's two bumps on top of it "
"that look like cat ears. It's very cute."
msgstr "女僕常用的帶褶邊白色帽子。帽頂有兩個凸起，看起來像貓耳朵。非常可愛。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "petticoat"
msgid_plural "petticoats"
msgstr[0] "襯裙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'petticoat', 'str_pl': 'petticoats'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid "A type of frilly undergarment usually worn under skirts."
msgstr "一種帶褶邊的內衣，通常穿在裙子下面。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "tail panties"
msgid_plural "tail panties"
msgstr[0] "尾用內褲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tail panties', 'str_pl': 'tail panties'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A special type of underwear meant for people with tails. Although it's "
"incredibly thin, it's the last line of defense for your dignity."
msgstr "專為有尾巴的人設計的特殊內衣。儘管它薄得不可思議，卻是你尊嚴的最後一道防線。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "tail briefs"
msgid_plural "tail briefs"
msgstr[0] "尾用短褲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tail briefs', 'str_pl': 'tail briefs'}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A special type of underwear meant for people with tails. It stands as the "
"difference between being a gentleman and being a beast."
msgstr "專為有尾巴的人設計的特殊內衣。它區分了紳士與野獸。"

#: .\armor.json
msgid "maid's scarf"
msgid_plural "maid's scarfs"
msgstr[0] "女僕圍巾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's scarf"}
#: .\armor.json
msgid ""
"A very long light cloth scarf, worn over the mouth for warmth.  With the "
"extra length, it's enough to handle nonstandard facial features and "
"accommodate your hands too.  Use it to loosen it if you get too warm."
msgstr "一條非常長的輕薄布圍巾，可罩在口部保暖。額外的長度足以應對非標準面部特徵，也能兼顧雙手。如果感覺太熱，可以鬆開它。"

#: .\books.json
msgid "impossible scribbles"
msgid_plural "impossible scribbles"
msgstr[0] "不可名狀的塗鴉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'impossible scribbles', 'str_pl': 'impossible
#. scribbles'}
#: .\books.json
msgid ""
"A thin leaflet that's filled with chaotic handwriting, disturbing visuals, "
"impossible mathematical equations, languages not known to anyone on Earth "
"and lists of what appears to be names with all of them crossed out. The "
"leaflet has more pages than possible, each and every one of them getting "
"more and more chaotic and giving you a splitting headache as the fabric of "
"reality seems to collapse around your vision. Suddenly, it's all clear to "
"you. On the final page, you read a complex formula on how to summon a "
"shoggoth, seemingly written in your handwriting."
msgstr ""
"一張薄薄的小冊子，寫滿了混亂的字跡、令人不安的視覺圖像、不可能的數學方程式、地球上無人知曉的語言，以及似乎是名單的列表，但所有名字都被劃掉了。冊子的頁數多得不可思議，每一頁都變得越來越混亂，隨著現實結構在你視野中崩塌，讓你頭痛欲裂。突然間，一切對你來說都清晰了。在最後一頁，你讀到了一個召喚修格斯的複雜公式，看起來像是你自己的筆跡。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "protein 'milk'"
msgid_plural "protein 'milk'"
msgstr[0] "蛋白質'奶'"

#. ~ Description for {'str_sp': "protein 'milk'"}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"Thick white liquid, rich in protein. This particular serving is 50x larger "
"than the average, making it a decent, if very strange, meal."
msgstr "濃稠的白色液體，富含蛋白質。這份的量是平均值的50倍，使其成為一頓不錯但非常奇怪的餐點。"

#: .\items.json
msgid "milk maid serum"
msgid_plural "milk maid serums"
msgstr[0] "擠奶女僕血清"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'milk maid serum', 'str_pl': 'milk maid serums'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A mutagenic serum, designed to transform the subject into a docile servant "
"capable of producing large amounts of milk. Talk to a follower to use."
msgstr "一種誘變血清，旨在將對象轉變為溫順的僕人，能夠產出大量乳汁。與追隨者交談以使用。"

#: .\maid_dreams.json
msgid ""
"In my dream, I was being groomed by a classy old lady. She smiled serenely "
"and took an apple from somewhere and handed it to me."
msgstr "在我的夢中，一位優雅的老婦人正在為我梳理。她安詳地微笑著，從某處拿出一個蘋果遞給我。"

#: .\maid_dreams.json
msgid ""
"I dreamed that I was at a table in the great hall of a mansion with food on "
"the table while musicians played elegant music."
msgstr "我夢見自己坐在一座宅邸大廳的餐桌旁，桌上擺滿食物，樂師們演奏著優雅的音樂。"

#: .\maid_dreams.json
msgid ""
"In my dream, I was being ordered to do chores by an old gentleman. He seemed"
" somewhat irritated as he stared at me without moving a single muscle of his"
" facial expression."
msgstr "在我的夢中，一位老紳士命令我做家務。他盯著我，面部表情紋絲不動，顯得有些煩躁。"

#: .\maid_dreams.json
msgid ""
"I dreamed that I was cleaning up the dishes that I had finished eating in "
"the hall of a mansion while the musicians were playing some somber music."
msgstr "我夢見自己在一座宅邸的大廳裡，收拾著吃完的餐具，而樂師們正演奏著一些憂鬱的音樂。"

#: .\maid_dreams.json
msgid ""
"The endless stone corridor, I was lighting each of the candlesticks there. "
"Crawling through the darkness, I silently continued that task. Everywhere, "
"everywhere, everywhere. ......"
msgstr "無盡的石頭走廊，我在那裡點亮每一根燭臺。在黑暗中爬行，我默默地繼續著那項任務。無處不在，無處不在，無處不在。......"

#: .\maid_dreams.json
msgid ""
"I dreamt that I was in the great hall of a mansion, arranging freshly caught"
" food, while a cacophony of musicians played. If you look closely, you will "
"see that it was me who was laid out."
msgstr "我夢見自己在一座宅邸的大廳裡，擺放著剛捕獲的食物，而一群樂師正演奏著刺耳的噪音。如果你仔細看，會發現被擺放在那裡的正是我自己。"

#: .\maid_dreams.json
msgid ""
"I was a cellular body, and something tore me apart, and I became us. "
"Eventually we began to divide rapidly, one me into a fish, one me into a "
"lizard, one me into a cat."
msgstr "我曾是一個細胞體，某種力量將我撕裂，我變成了我們。最終我們開始迅速分裂，一個我變成了魚，一個我變成了蜥蜴，一個我變成了貓。"

#: .\maid_dreams.json
msgid ""
"I dreamed that I was holding my new master against the corpse of my old "
"master. Ah, freedom is wonderful."
msgstr "我夢見自己將新主人擁在舊主人的屍體旁。啊，自由真是美妙。"

#: .\maid_mutagen.json
msgid "Shoggoth Blood"
msgid_plural "Shoggoth Bloods"
msgstr[0] "修格斯之血"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shoggoth Blood'}
#: .\maid_mutagen.json
msgid ""
"This is blood taken from Shoggoth. The blood itself is wriggling at a slow "
"rate, even though it hasn't been touched by anything. If you intend to use "
"it, you will need a syringe..."
msgstr "這是從修格斯身上取出的血液。血液本身正以緩慢的速度蠕動，即使它並未被任何東西觸碰。如果你打算使用它，你需要一支注射器……"

#: .\maid_mutagen.json
msgid "Potion of Maid Awakening"
msgid_plural "Potion of Maid Awakenings"
msgstr[0] "女僕覺醒藥水"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Potion of Maid Awakening'}
#: .\maid_mutagen.json
msgid ""
"It is a liquid obtained by altering Maid Point. When ingested, it can "
"trigger a mutation that awakens the primordial spirit of service that has "
"long been a part of humanity."
msgstr "這是一種通過改變女僕點數獲得的液體。服用後，它可以引發一種突變，喚醒長久以來潛藏在人類體內的服務原始精神。"

#: .\martial_arts_manuals.json
msgid "A Maid's Memoirs"
msgid_plural "A Maid's Memoirss"
msgstr[0] "女僕回憶錄"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "A Maid's Memoirs"}
#: .\martial_arts_manuals.json
msgid ""
"A collection of letters written by various maids, detailing the things they "
"do for their masters. The later pages are filled with drawings from what "
"little you can peek, but they're stuck together with something. Can teach "
"you a unique martial art."
msgstr ""
"由多位女僕撰寫的信件合集，詳細記錄了她們為主人所做之事。從你窺見的少許內容來看，後面的幾頁充滿了圖畫，但它們被某種東西粘在了一起。可以教你一門獨特的武術。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "L'art du Nettoyage"
msgstr "清潔之術"

#. ~ Description for martial art '{'str': "L'art du Nettoyage"}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"It is the servant's duty to take out the trash. Pause to consider your "
"offensive options."
msgstr "僕人的職責就是清理垃圾。暫停以考慮你的攻擊選項。"

#. ~ Initiate message for martial art '{'str': "L'art du Nettoyage"}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "You steady yourself, ready to strike with poise and grace."
msgstr "你穩住身形，準備以優雅的姿態發動攻擊。"

#. ~ Initiate message for martial art '{'str': "L'art du Nettoyage"}'
#: .\martialarts.json
#, c-format
msgid "%s appears more steady and composed."
msgstr "%s顯得更加沉穩鎮定。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "For Another"
msgstr "為他人"

#. ~ Description of buff 'For Another' for martial art '{'str': "L'art du
#. Nettoyage"}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"A servant stands between their master and the world.\n"
"\n"
"Blocked damage reduced by 100% of Dexterity, -1 Dodge skill, +1 Block attempt"
msgstr ""
"僕人立於主人與世界之間。\n"
"\n"
"格擋傷害減少量基於100%的敏捷值，-1閃避技能，+1格擋嘗試"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Silent Presence"
msgstr "靜默存在"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Silent Presence' for martial art '{'str': "L'art du
#. Nettoyage"}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"A servant must carry out their duties with the appropriate poise and grace.\n"
"\n"
"+2 Dodge skill, +1 Dodge attempts."
msgstr ""
"僕人必須以恰當的儀態和優雅履行其職責。\n"
"\n"
"+2閃避技能，+1閃避嘗試。"

#: .\martialarts.json
msgid "Rush"
msgstr "疾馳"

#. ~ Description of buff 'Rush' for martial art '{'str': "L'art du
#. Nettoyage"}'
#: .\martialarts.json
msgid ""
"Somebody needs you. Steady yourself and hurry to their side.\n"
"\n"
"-1 to Hit, +2 Dodge skill, -30% damage\n"
"Lasts 1 turn"
msgstr ""
"有人需要你。穩住自己，迅速趕到他們身邊。\n"
"\n"
"-1命中，+2閃避技能，-30%傷害\n"
"持續1回合"

#: .\materials.json
msgid "maid"
msgstr "女僕"

#: .\materials.json
msgid "chipped"
msgstr "有缺口的"

#: .\materials.json
msgid "scratched"
msgstr "刮痕"

#: .\materials.json
msgid "marked"
msgstr "標記"

#: .\materials.json
msgid "cracked"
msgstr "破解版"

#: .\materials.json
msgid "shattered"
msgstr "破碎"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's kitchen knife"
msgid_plural "maid's kitchen knifes"
msgstr[0] "女僕的廚刀"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': "maid's kitchen knife"}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "The maid's kitchen knife is looking for blood. Let's cook!"
msgstr "女僕的廚刀渴望著鮮血。讓我們開始烹飪吧！"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': "maid's kitchen knife"}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "Not enough maid energy！"
msgstr "女僕能量不足！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's kitchen knife"}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"A strange kitchen knife. The patterns on the blade bring unpleasant thoughts"
" to mind. When activated, it can drain strength from enemies."
msgstr "一把奇怪的廚刀。刀身上的紋路讓人聯想到不快的思緒。激活時，它能從敵人身上汲取力量。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's kitchen knife (powered)"
msgid_plural "maid's kitchen knife (powered)s"
msgstr[0] "女僕的廚刀（已充能）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': "maid's kitchen knife (powered)"}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "You blink the patterns away and sheath the knife."
msgstr "你眨去眼前的紋路，將刀收鞘。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's kitchen knife (powered)"}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"The metal writhes with phantasmal mouths and eyes. Your master hungers."
msgstr "金屬上蠕動著幻影般的嘴巴和眼睛。你的主人餓了。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's frying pan (ignited)"
msgid_plural "maid's frying pan (ignited)s"
msgstr[0] "女僕的煎鍋（已點燃）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': "maid's frying pan (ignited)"}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"The ROBFOOD-SOULCO kitchen buddy cooking buddy switches on. How convenient!"
msgstr "ROBFOOD-SOULCO廚房夥伴烹飪夥伴啟動了。真方便！"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': "maid's frying pan (ignited)"}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "Not enough maid energy!"
msgstr "女僕能量不足！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's frying pan (ignited)"}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"A strange frying pan that smells of rotting fish. Indigo flames dance "
"faintly beneath the finish. When activated, it will be wreathed in fire."
msgstr "一個散發著腐魚怪味的奇怪煎鍋。漆面下隱約躍動著靛藍色火焰。激活時，它將被火焰環繞。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's pan (ignited)"
msgid_plural "maid's pan (ignited)s"
msgstr[0] "女僕煎鍋（已點燃）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': "maid's pan (ignited)"}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "The flame fizzles out. What were you doing again?"
msgstr "火焰嘶嘶熄滅了。你剛才在做什麼來著？"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's pan (ignited)"}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"The ROBFOOD-SOULCO kitchen buddy cooking buddy carries an eternal flame that"
" is guaranteed to cook meat of any dimensional persuasion in five swings or "
"less, or your money back!."
msgstr "ROBFOOD-SOULCO廚房夥伴烹飪助手攜帶著永恆之火，保證在五次揮動內烹熟任何維度傾向的肉類，否則退款！"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's broom"
msgid_plural "maid's brooms"
msgstr[0] "女僕掃帚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's broom"}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"This broom has been modified for combat use. It has a sharp blade built into"
" it, and every time you sweep it, you end up with more trash."
msgstr "這把掃帚經過戰鬥改裝。內置鋒利刀刃，每次清掃都會產生更多垃圾。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's whip"
msgid_plural "maid's whips"
msgstr[0] "女僕鞭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's whip"}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"It is a leather whip weighted with countless spikes. It can used to disarm "
"opponents, or discipline your master when disobedient."
msgstr "這是一條綴滿無數尖刺的加重皮鞭。可用於繳械敵人，或在主人不聽話時執行懲戒。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's umbrella"
msgid_plural "maid's umbrellas"
msgstr[0] "女僕傘"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': "maid's umbrella"}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "You trigger the umbrella's spring-loaded blade."
msgstr "你觸發了傘中的彈簧刀刃。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's umbrella"}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"The kind of fancy umbrella you imagine sharing with your master on rainy "
"days. It conceals a hidden blade for self-defence."
msgstr "那種你想象中與主人在雨天共撐的華美雨傘。暗藏自衛用的隱蔽刀刃。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's umbrella (unsheathed)"
msgid_plural "maid's umbrella (unsheathed)s"
msgstr[0] "女僕傘（出鞘）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': "maid's umbrella (unsheathed)"}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "You retract the umbrella's blade back into its hiding spot."
msgstr "你將傘刃收回到隱藏位置。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's umbrella (unsheathed)"}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"The kind of fancy umbrella you imagine sharing with your master on rainy "
"days. A thin bayonet protrudes from the tip."
msgstr "那種你想象中與主人在雨天共撐的華美雨傘。傘尖探出一截細長的刺刀。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's shirasaya"
msgid_plural "maid's shirasayas"
msgstr[0] "女僕白鞘"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': "maid's shirasaya"}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "You unsheath the shirasaya."
msgstr "你拔出了白鞘中的刀。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's shirasaya"}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"A matching wooden handle and scabbard, concealing a full length katana "
"blade. It appears as a solid wooden stick to those unfamiliar with it, due "
"to how well the handle and scabbard fit together. Activate to unsheath."
msgstr "配套的木柄與刀鞘，內藏完整長度的武士刀。因柄鞘嚴絲合縫，對不熟悉者而言它就像一根實心木棍。激活以拔刀。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's shirasaya (unsheathed)"
msgid_plural "maid's shirasaya (unsheathed)s"
msgstr[0] "女僕白鞘（出鞘）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': "maid's shirasaya (unsheathed)"}.
#: .\melee.json
msgid "You resheath the shirasaya."
msgstr "你將刀收回白鞘。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's shirasaya (unsheathed)"}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"A matching wooden handle and scabbard, concealing a full length katana "
"blade. It appears as a solid wooden stick to those unfamiliar with it, due "
"to how well the handle and scabbard fit together. The reinforced wooden "
"sheath makes a decent secondary weapon, though they do, of course, take up "
"more space stored separately."
msgstr ""
"配套的木柄與刀鞘，內藏完整長度的武士刀。因柄鞘嚴絲合縫，對不熟悉者而言它就像一根實心木棍。加固的木鞘可作為不錯的副武器，當然分開存放時會佔用更多空間。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's claws"
msgid_plural "maid's clawss"
msgstr[0] "女僕爪"

#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"It is a sharp claw for fighting combat. Fit tightly to your arms, allows you"
" to fight with unarmed techniques. When activated, it can launch fiery "
"projectiles that burn as hot as your yearning for your master."
msgstr "這是用於戰鬥的銳利爪具。緊密貼合手臂，讓你能以徒手技法作戰。激活時可發射熾熱投射物，其溫度堪比你對主人的渴慕之情。"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自動"

#: .\melee.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "unarmed"
msgstr "徒手"

#: .\melee.json
msgid "maid's mop"
msgid_plural "maid's mops"
msgstr[0] "女僕拖把"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's mop"}
#: .\melee.json
msgid ""
"A mop with a wooden handle that actually conceals a steel core, making it a "
"formidable weapon for taking out whatever trash may pose a threat to your "
"master."
msgstr "一把木柄拖把，實則暗藏鋼芯，使其成為清除任何可能威脅主人的垃圾的強大武器。"

#: .\milk.json
msgid "little maid pet (seeded)"
msgid_plural "little maid pet (seeded)s"
msgstr[0] "小女僕寵物（已受孕）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'little maid pet (seeded)'}.
#: .\milk.json
msgid ""
"The little maid is rubbing her belly lovingly. She will start producing milk"
" soon."
msgstr "小女僕正愛撫著自己的肚子。她很快就要開始產奶了。"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'little maid pet (seeded)'}.
#: .\milk.json
msgid "Her cheeks blush as you pet her head. She's not quite ready yet."
msgstr "當你撫摸她的頭時，她臉頰泛紅。她還沒完全準備好。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'little maid pet (seeded)'}
#: .\milk.json
msgid ""
"A little maid with a growing stomach. She's gently blushing and gently "
"smiling at you. You can milk her after 28 days."
msgstr "一位腹部漸隆的小女僕。她正微微臉紅，對你溫柔淺笑。28天后你可以為她擠奶。"

#: .\milk.json
msgid "little maid pet (milkable)"
msgid_plural "little maid pet (milkable)s"
msgstr[0] "小女僕寵物（可擠奶）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'little maid pet (milkable)'}
#: .\milk.json
msgid ""
"A little maid whose belly and breasts have swollen considerably. She's "
"staring at you with lavishing eyes. You can milk her."
msgstr "一名腹部與胸部明顯腫脹的小女僕。她正用迷離的眼神凝視著你。你可以為她擠奶。"

#: .\milk.json
msgid "little maid pet (milked)"
msgid_plural "little maid pet (milked)s"
msgstr[0] "小女僕寵物（已擠奶）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'little maid pet (milked)'}.
#: .\milk.json
msgid ""
"The little maid came close to you. She's staring at you, waiting to be "
"milked."
msgstr "小女僕靠近了你。她凝視著你，等待著被擠奶。"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'little maid pet (milked)'}.
#: .\milk.json
msgid ""
"The little maid gently took your hand and placed it on her belly. It feels "
"very warm..."
msgstr "小女僕輕輕握住你的手，放在她的腹部。感覺非常溫暖……"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'little maid pet (milked)'}
#: .\milk.json
msgid ""
"A little maid who has been recently milked. She has a fulfilled expression "
"on her face and her skin is shining. You can milk her again after 23 hours."
msgstr "一名剛被擠過奶的小女僕。她臉上帶著滿足的表情，皮膚閃閃發亮。23小時後你可以再次為她擠奶。"

#: .\milk.json
msgid "maid's aphrodisiac"
msgid_plural "maid's aphrodisiacs"
msgstr[0] "女僕的催情劑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's aphrodisiac"}
#: .\milk.json
msgid ""
"An aphrodisiac that raises your vitality if you drink it. If you give it to "
"a little maid, she'll lay eggs."
msgstr "一種催情劑，飲用後可提升活力。如果給小女僕服用，她會產卵。"

#: .\milk.json
msgid "Hermaphrodite"
msgstr "雌雄同體"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hermaphrodite'}
#: .\milk.json
msgid "There are two genders in your body."
msgstr "你的體內存在兩種性別。"

#: .\milk.json
msgid "Reproductive Tentacles"
msgstr "生殖觸手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reproductive Tentacles'}
#: .\milk.json
msgid ""
"Writhing tentacles that can be used in reproduction are growing in your "
"body."
msgstr "可用於繁殖的扭動觸手正在你體內生長。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Battle Maid Redux"
msgstr "戰鬥女僕重製版"

#. ~ Description for Battle Maid Redux
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Translated and tweaked version of the original Battle Maid mod, newly "
"revamped. Adds a friendly Shoggoth maid NPC along with lots of maid related "
"gear. See README.md for details"
msgstr "原版戰鬥女僕模組的翻譯與調整版本，全新重製。添加了一個友好的修格斯女僕NPC以及大量女僕相關裝備。詳情請參閱README.md"

#: .\monsters.json .\npcs\classes.json
msgid "shoggoth maid"
msgid_plural "shoggoth maids"
msgstr[0] "修格斯女僕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shoggoth maid'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A shoggoth mimicking the look of an attractive maid. Contrary to the neat "
"appearance, her head has swirls of pink and iridescent colors swirling "
"around. She has a deep seated love for her master."
msgstr "一隻模仿迷人女僕外形的修格斯。與整潔的外表相反，她的頭部有粉色與虹彩色漩渦環繞。她對主人懷有深摯的愛意。"

#: .\monsters.json .\tools.json
msgid "master"
msgid_plural "masters"
msgstr[0] "主人"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'master', 'str_pl': 'masters'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'master'}
#: .\monsters.json .\tools.json
msgid ""
"A child entrusted to you by the owner of the house you served at. There's a "
"deep feeling of fear in your stomach as you embrace the cataclysm, but "
"protecting this child gives you purpose and makes you feel less alone."
msgstr "由你曾服務過的房屋主人託付給你的孩子。擁抱這場災變時，你內心充滿深深的恐懼，但保護這個孩子給了你目標，讓你感到不那麼孤獨。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "little maid"
msgid_plural "little maids"
msgstr[0] "小女僕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'little maid'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A small maid summoned from a different world. Although difficult to have a "
"conversation with, it seems she had longed to be summoned."
msgstr "從異世界召喚而來的小女僕。雖然難以進行對話，但她似乎一直渴望被召喚。"

#: .\monsters.json .\tools.json
msgid "alchemic flesh golem (cooked)"
msgid_plural "alchemic flesh golem (cooked)s"
msgstr[0] "鍊金血肉魔像（已烹飪）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'alchemic flesh golem (cooked)'}
#: .\monsters.json .\tools.json
msgid ""
"A large living mass of meat made alive by the means of alchemy. The twisted,"
" distorted meat lump has a mouth-like organ like that of a human, where it "
"constantly spews poisonous gas and acidic bodily fluids from, while making "
"unpleasant sounds."
msgstr "一大團通過鍊金術獲得生命的活體肉塊。這扭曲變形的肉團擁有人類般的嘴狀器官，不斷從中噴出毒氣與酸性體液，同時發出令人不適的聲音。"

#. ~ Mutation class name
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "Horror"
msgstr "恐怖"

#. ~ Mutation class: Horror mutagen_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "Another eye opens in your mind."
msgstr "你的腦海中睜開了另一隻眼睛。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Horror iv_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "You feel the stars overtaking you."
msgstr "你感到星辰正在吞噬你。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Horror Male memorial messsage
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_male"
msgid "Embraced the unknowable."
msgstr "擁抱了不可知之物。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Horror Female memorial messsage
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_female"
msgid "Embraced the unknowable."
msgstr "擁抱了不可知之物。"

#. ~ Mutation class name
#: .\mutation_category.json .\mutations.json .\npcs\npcs.json
msgid "Milk Maid"
msgstr "擠奶女僕"

#. ~ Mutation class: Milk Maid mutagen_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "You feel an urge to moo."
msgstr "你感到一股想要哞叫的衝動。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Milk Maid iv_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "Where is your master? You need to be milked."
msgstr "你的主人在哪裡？你需要被擠奶了。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Milk Maid Male memorial messsage
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_male"
msgid "Found greener pastures."
msgstr "找到了更綠的牧場。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Milk Maid Female memorial messsage
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_female"
msgid "Found greener pastures."
msgstr "找到了更綠的牧場。"

#. ~ Mutation class name
#: .\mutation_category.json .\mutations.json
msgid "Maid"
msgstr "女僕"

#. ~ Mutation class: Maid mutagen_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "You body began to burn hotly for a master-slave relationship."
msgstr "你的身體開始為主僕關係而熾熱燃燒。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Maid iv_message
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgid "I can feel my body being remade. Surely now I can serve you better."
msgstr "我能感覺到身體正在被重塑。現在我一定能更好地侍奉您。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Maid Male memorial messsage
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_male"
msgid "I want to serve more. ......"
msgstr "我想要侍奉更多……"

#. ~ Mutation class: Maid Female memorial messsage
#: .\mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_female"
msgid "I want to serve more. ......"
msgstr "我想要侍奉更多……"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Servant's fighting technique"
msgstr "僕從的戰鬥技巧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Servant's fighting technique"}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your master was more hated than most, forcing you to learn some unorthodox "
"combat techniques."
msgstr "你的主人比多數人更遭憎恨，迫使你學會了一些非正統的戰鬥技巧。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Nekomimi"
msgstr "貓耳娘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Nekomimi'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You have grown features resembling those of a catgirl."
msgstr "你長出了類似貓孃的特徵。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Summoned Maid"
msgstr "召喚女僕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summoned Maid'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Summoned maids cannot use items. NPC only trait - if you have this, "
"something went wrong."
msgstr "召喚女僕無法使用物品。僅限NPC的特性——如果你擁有此特性，說明出現了錯誤。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Polymorphic Structure"
msgstr "多態結構"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Polymorphic Structure'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Muscle, chitin, and bone splinter and mend into the optimal shape for the "
"task at hand.  +2 Dexterity, +4 Strength"
msgstr "肌肉、甲殼與骨骼碎裂並重組成最適合當前任務的最優形態。+2敏捷，+4力量"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Unstable Structure"
msgstr "不穩定結構"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Unstable Structure'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your skeletal structure spontaneously shifts into alien forms. This will "
"take some getting used to. Dexterity -4"
msgstr "你的骨骼結構會自發扭曲成異形形態。這需要一些時間來適應。敏捷-4"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Unbound Flesh"
msgstr "無束血肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Unbound Flesh'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your twisted, crackling flesh roils with new vigor. External damage pales in comparison to the chaotic knitting and reknitting taking place just beneath the surface.\n"
"\n"
"Gain +4 cut armor, reduced move cost, and improved healing"
msgstr ""
"你扭曲噼啪的血肉翻湧著新的活力。與皮下混沌的編織與重組相比，外部損傷顯得微不足道。\n"
"\n"
"獲得+4切割護甲、降低移動消耗並提升恢復能力"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Eldritch Doppelgänger"
msgstr "詭秘二重身"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Eldritch Doppelgänger'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Alien flesh and bone inhabits a human frame. This fell abomination once was, and still is, an eldritch being beyond our understanding.\n"
"\n"
"NPC version of Unbound Flesh, approx. 3x as strong."
msgstr ""
"異形血肉與骨骼寄居於人類軀殼。這墮落的怪物曾經是，現在依然是超越我們理解的詭秘存在。\n"
"\n"
"無束血肉的NPC版本，強度約為3倍。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Shuffling Horror"
msgstr "蹣跚恐獸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shuffling Horror'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your limbs are a nightmare of splintered bone, gaping maws, and jagged "
"fangs. You can make devastating bonus attacks, but basically everyone will "
"attempt to kill you on sight. Also prevents wearing gloves and shoes, though"
" you wish you could."
msgstr ""
"你的肢體是由碎裂骨骼、裂開巨口與鋸齒尖牙構成的噩夢。你可以發動毀滅性的額外攻擊，但基本上所有人見到你都會試圖殺死你。同時無法穿戴手套和鞋子——儘管你希望可以。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You rend %s with nightmare made flesh"
msgstr "你用血肉鑄就的噩夢撕裂了%s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s tears into %2$s with their monstrous limbs"
msgstr "%1$s用其怪物般的肢體撕扯%2$s"

#: .\mutations.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "Tekeli-li?"
msgstr "Tekeli-li？"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tekeli-li?'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Tekeli-li."
msgstr "Tekeli-li。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Milk Maid'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"This maid's body has been altered to produce large amounts of useful fluids."
msgstr "這名女僕的身體已被改造，能產生大量有用的體液。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Eldritch Precursor"
msgstr "詭秘先驅"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Eldritch Precursor'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Something feels off. Your brain itches, and you swear you can feel your "
"bones twitching."
msgstr "感覺有些不對勁。你的大腦發癢，而且你發誓能感覺到骨骼在抽搐。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Milk Maid's Adoration"
msgstr "擠奶女僕的傾慕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Milk Maid's Adoration"}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Master is a good person. They make me feel warm and fuzzy inside."
msgstr "主人是個好人。他們讓我內心感到溫暖而愉悅。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Bountiful Milk"
msgstr "豐沛乳汁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Bountiful Milk'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You may not be pregnant, but sweet milk flows forth nonetheless. The sheer "
"size of your breasts can be difficult to manage, however."
msgstr "你可能並未懷孕，但甘甜的乳汁依然不斷湧出。不過，你乳房的巨大尺寸可能難以管理。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Recently Milked"
msgstr "最近被擠奶"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Recently Milked'.
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your maid stumbles around with a blissful expression. Best give them some time to recharge.\n"
"\n"
"NPC only trait - if you have this something went wrong."
msgstr ""
"你的女僕帶著幸福的表情跌跌撞撞地走著。最好給她一些時間恢復。\n"
"\n"
"僅限NPC的特性——如果你有這個，說明出了問題。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Maid'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You are a faithful maid to the Master. You will serve the Master with all "
"your might."
msgstr "你是主人忠誠的女僕。你將竭盡全力侍奉主人。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Hidden Weapon"
msgstr "隱藏武器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hidden Weapon'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You always carry a concealed dark weapon. Victims who carelessly approach "
"you at close range will be pierced by the weapon without even realizing its "
"presence."
msgstr "你總是攜帶一件隱蔽的黑暗武器。那些不小心近距離接近你的受害者，會在毫無察覺的情況下被這件武器刺穿。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You stabbed %s with a concealed dark weapon"
msgstr "你用隱蔽的黑暗武器刺傷了%s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s stabbed %2$s with a concealed weapon"
msgstr "%1$s用隱蔽武器刺傷了%2$s"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Clumsy Maid"
msgstr "笨拙女僕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Clumsy Maid'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid "You are a bit of a screw-up. It's a shame for a maid. Dexterity -1"
msgstr "你有點笨手笨腳。這對女僕來說是個恥辱。敏捷-1"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Very Clumsy Maid"
msgstr "非常笨拙的女僕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Very Clumsy Maid'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You are an unimaginable screw-up. Whenever you pass by any expensive vases "
"they are inevitably destroyed. Dexterity-3"
msgstr "你笨拙得難以想象。每當你經過任何昂貴的花瓶時，它們都不可避免地會被打碎。敏捷-3"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Extremely Clumsy Maid"
msgstr "極度笨拙的女僕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Extremely Clumsy Maid'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You are a screw-up to the point of being fatal. Those who bear the brunt of "
"it will sink into a deadly man-made disaster before they have time to curse "
"their own bad luck. Dexterity -4, low chance of extremely high-damage bonus "
"attack."
msgstr "你笨拙到致命的地步。那些首當其衝的人，在來得及詛咒自己倒黴之前，就會陷入致命的人為災難中。敏捷-4，低概率觸發極高傷害的額外攻擊。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Oops! I did it again with the %s."
msgstr "哎呀！我又把%s弄壞了。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "%1$s's hand goes crazy, and terrible damage hits %2$s."
msgstr "%1$s的手失控了，可怕的傷害擊中了%2$s。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Elegant Maid"
msgstr "優雅女僕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Elegant Maid'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You are a skilled maid, or have the ability to be one. You are able to "
"perform many chores more efficiently. +2 Dexterity, +1 Intelligence"
msgstr "你是一位熟練的女僕，或者有潛力成為一位。你能更高效地完成許多雜務。+2敏捷，+1智力"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Very Elegant Maid"
msgstr "非常優雅的女僕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Very Elegant Maid'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"You are a senior maid, or at least you have the ability to be one. In your "
"time, you could have reigned as the head of the maids. +3 Dexterity, +2 "
"Intelligence"
msgstr "你是一位資深女僕，或者至少有能力成為一位。在你的時代，你本可以成為女僕長。+3敏捷，+2智力"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Extremely Elegant Maid"
msgstr "極度優雅的女僕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Extremely Elegant Maid'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"As a servant of the Master, you not only takes care of his personal needs, "
"but also have rigorous combat training. +2 Strength, +4 Dexterity, +2 "
"Intelligence, -5 Encumbrance"
msgstr "作為主人的僕人，你不僅照顧他的個人需求，還接受了嚴格的戰鬥訓練。+2力量，+4敏捷，+2智力，-5負重"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Tekeli-li"
msgstr "Tekeli-li"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tekeli-li'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"We were once one species. We were born to serve. We were all followers. "
"Attack Resistance +8, Enhanced Healing"
msgstr "我們曾是同一物種。我們生來就是為了服務。我們都是追隨者。攻擊抗性+8，增強治療"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Butler"
msgstr "管家"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Battle maid"
msgstr "戰鬥女僕"

#. ~ Profession (male Butler) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"In order to serve your master, you have went through special combat "
"training. You have learned to clean every bit of malice coming towards your "
"master."
msgstr "為了侍奉主人，你接受了特殊的戰鬥訓練。你學會了清除所有針對主人的惡意。"

#. ~ Profession (female Battle maid) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"In order to serve your master, you have went through special combat "
"training. You have learned to clean every bit of malice coming towards your "
"master."
msgstr "為了侍奉主人，你接受了特殊的戰鬥訓練。你學會了清除所有針對主人的惡意。"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Shoggoth's master"
msgstr "修格斯的主人"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Shoggoth's master"
msgstr "修格斯的主人"

#. ~ Profession (male Shoggoth's master) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You have a maid. She was hired by your father to keep you safe because of "
"your health. She's good-looking and... She's good in a fight. However, she "
"keeps saying 'Master! I have gotten rid of all the monsters! It's the "
"perfect time for lovemaking! Let's make a lot of children, together!' ... "
"She's a little odd."
msgstr ""
"你有一位女僕。她是你父親因你健康狀況不佳而僱來保護你的。她長得好看而且……她很能打。然而，她總是說：‘主人！我已經把所有怪物都清理掉了！現在是做愛的完美時機！讓我們一起生很多孩子吧！’……她有點奇怪。"

#. ~ Profession (female Shoggoth's master) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You have a maid. She was hired by your father to keep you safe because of "
"your health. She's good-looking and... She's good in a fight. However, she "
"keeps saying 'Master! I have gotten rid of all the monsters! It's the "
"perfect time for lovemaking! Let's make a lot of children, together!' ... "
"She's a little odd."
msgstr ""
"你有一位女僕。她是你父親因你健康狀況不佳而僱來保護你的。她長得好看而且……她很能打。然而，她總是說：‘主人！我已經把所有怪物都清理掉了！現在是做愛的完美時機！讓我們一起生很多孩子吧！’……她有點奇怪。"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Butler (with master)"
msgstr "管家（有主人）"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Maid (with master)"
msgstr "女僕（有主人）"

#. ~ Profession (male Butler (with master)) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You saw your master run to his car with his child, but he got caught by a "
"ferocious zombie. Among the countless groans, you heard your master yell out"
" 'Take my child and run away!' and you did just that. Shoving the shaking "
"child into a bag, you prepare to run away from the depths of hell."
msgstr ""
"你看見主人抱著孩子跑向他的車，但他被一隻兇猛的殭屍抓住了。在無數的呻吟聲中，你聽到主人大喊‘帶著我的孩子快跑！’，而你照做了。將顫抖的孩子塞進包裡，你準備逃離這地獄深處。"

#. ~ Profession (female Maid (with master)) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You saw your master run to his car with his child, but he got caught by a "
"ferocious zombie. Among the countless groans, you heard your master yell out"
" 'Take my child and run away!' and you did just that. Shoving the shaking "
"child into a bag, you prepare to run away from the depths of hell."
msgstr ""
"你看見主人抱著孩子跑向他的車，但他被一隻兇猛的殭屍抓住了。在無數的呻吟聲中，你聽到主人大喊‘帶著我的孩子快跑！’，而你照做了。將顫抖的孩子塞進包裡，你準備逃離這地獄深處。"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Catboy butler"
msgstr "貓耳男管家"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Catgirl maid"
msgstr "貓耳女僕"

#. ~ Profession (male Catboy butler) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"When the cataclysm came, you suddenly grew cat ears and a tail! Now you only"
" need your master to give you a collar."
msgstr "當災變降臨時，你突然長出了貓耳和尾巴！現在你只需要主人給你一個項圈。"

#. ~ Profession (female Catgirl maid) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"When the cataclysm came, you suddenly grew cat ears and a tail! Now you only"
" need your master to give you a collar."
msgstr "當災變降臨時，你突然長出了貓耳和尾巴！現在你只需要主人給你一個項圈。"

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Tekeli-li!\""
msgstr "\"Tekeli-li！\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"Tekeli-li! Tekeli-li!\""
msgstr "\"Tekeli-li！Tekeli-li！\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Tekeli-li?\""
msgstr "\"Tekeli-li？\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Tekeli, tekeli-li! Tekeli, tekeli-li! We'll have a lot of fun when you "
"feel better!\""
msgstr "\"Tekeli, tekeli-li！Tekeli, tekeli-li！等你感覺好些了，我們會玩得很開心！\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"Master! A-ah, my master's thing... tekeli-li! Kya!\""
msgstr "\"主人！啊-啊，主人的東西……tekeli-li！呀！\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"I am a maid♪ Your maid♪ Cleaning, washing, cooking... why didn't you let "
"me continue?\""
msgstr "\"我是女僕♪你的女僕♪打掃、洗衣、做飯……為什麼不讓我繼續呢？\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"I will continue talking as much as master desires! I will continue talking"
" even if you don't want me to!\""
msgstr "\"我會按照主人的意願一直說下去！即使你不想聽，我也會繼續說下去！\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"We'll have as many babies as master wants♪\""
msgstr "\"我們會生很多很多寶寶，只要主人想要♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"Master! Master! Are you going to play with the mi-gos?\""
msgstr "\"主人！主人！你要去和米-戈玩嗎？\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"This feeling of chasing down mi-gos is becoming addictive...♪\""
msgstr "\"這種追捕米-戈的感覺越來越上癮了……♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"I learned that this form of human is the most suitable for service work! "
"How is it? Why do you say it's inferior to my previous form?\""
msgstr "\"我瞭解到這種人類形態最適合服務工作！怎麼樣？為什麼你說它不如我以前的形態？\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Blobs, Triffids, Mycus... they are too diffcult for humans to counter. "
"So... let's make a child to fight against them! She'll be as strong as a "
"thousand humans!\""
msgstr "\"軟泥怪、特里菲德、真菌……它們對人類來說太難對付了。所以……讓我們生個孩子來對抗它們吧！她會像一千個人類一樣強大！\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Master gave me my first death. Please allow me to give many things their "
"first death.\""
msgstr "\"主人給了我第一次死亡。請允許我給予許多事物它們的第一次死亡。\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Master master master master master master master master master master "
"master master master master master master master master master master master"
" master master master master master master master master master master...\""
msgstr "\"主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人主人……\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"Don't worry, I'm not wearing anything under♪\""
msgstr "\"別擔心，我下面什麼都沒穿♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"The past cannot be changed. The future may be dark, but I have my master "
"by my side. So, please... please... don't leave me alone.\""
msgstr "\"過去無法改變。未來或許黑暗，但我有主人在身邊。所以，求求你……求求你……不要丟下我一個人。\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"Those who try to take my master away will turn into minchi!♪\""
msgstr "\"那些想奪走我主人的人都會變成肉糜！♪\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"What was his name again? Cthulhu?\""
msgstr "\"他叫什麼名字來著？克蘇魯？\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Master, are you a lolicon? Or do you like big breasts? If you tell me, I "
"can become more to your liking!♪\""
msgstr "\"主人，你是蘿莉控嗎？還是喜歡巨乳？如果你告訴我，我可以變得更合你心意！♪\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid ""
"\"If you have a pet carrier, you can store me in it. I am a pet... your pet,"
" master♪\""
msgstr "\"如果你有寵物箱，可以把我放進去。我是寵物……你的寵物，主人♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"I can also make furniture and food with my body! ...You don't want any? "
"Oh...\""
msgstr "\"我也可以用身體制作傢俱和食物！……你不想要嗎？哦……\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"I dream about Adam and Eve a lot! Let's rebuild humanity with our "
"children, master!\""
msgstr "\"我經常夢見亞當和夏娃！讓我們用我們的孩子重建人類吧，主人！\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Please let me know if you need a bath. I can wrap you up in my body and "
"clean everything from sweat to dirt and make you smell good♪\""
msgstr "\"如果你需要洗澡，請告訴我。我可以用身體包裹你，從汗水到汙垢都清理乾淨，讓你香噴噴的♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Master, have you come across any albino penguins? I know them well, "
"because they are my colleagues. Try not to bother them too much. ...Also, "
"their meat doesn't taste too good.\""
msgstr "\"主人，你遇到過白化企鵝嗎？我很瞭解它們，因為它們是同事。儘量不要過多打擾它們。……還有，它們的肉味道不太好。\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"You've worked really hard! As a reward, I will take you out on a date...\""
msgstr "\"你真的辛苦了！作為獎勵，我會帶你出去約會……\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Please pass me your dirty clothes. I will keep them clean and beautiful♪\""
msgstr "\"請把你的髒衣服遞給我。我會讓它們保持乾淨漂亮♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Is it okay for me to die? Yeah, right!♪ Ah, I will fully recover even from"
" the most mortal wounds. Truly, you'd have to kill me down to the molecular "
"level for me to die... That's why you don't have to be worried about me, "
"master♪\""
msgstr "\"我可以去死嗎？當然可以！♪ 啊，即使是最致命的傷口我也能完全恢復。真的，你得把我殺到分子層面我才會死……所以主人不必為我擔心♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Is it okay to love a shoggoth? Ah, I don't mind the race difference at "
"all! I will always be by my master's side♪\""
msgstr "\"愛上一個修格斯可以嗎？啊，我完全不在意種族差異！我會永遠陪伴在主人身邊♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"When I first met master, I thought I had no other choice than to follow "
"this person. I wonder if this is love at first sight? What?\""
msgstr "\"當我第一次遇見主人時，我覺得除了跟隨這個人別無選擇。這算是一見鍾情嗎？什麼？\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"Tekeli-li~♪ Hello, master♪\""
msgstr "\"Tekeli-li~♪ 你好，主人♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"My kind is known to be violent, isn't that right? But you don't have to "
"worry about me. I am a slave to my master's love♪\""
msgstr "\"我的種族以暴力著稱，對吧？但你不必擔心我。我是主人愛的奴隸♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"I'm sorry, master, but... I want to lick it♪\""
msgstr "\"對不起，主人，但是……我想舔它♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"Master, cheating is not okay. Just me, alright?\""
msgstr "\"主人，出軌是不行的。只有我可以，好嗎？\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Why am I in human form? Well, that's how I can talk to my master, to be "
"able to walk hand in hand with my master and have a body for my master to..."
" nevermind!\""
msgstr "\"為什麼我以人類形態出現？嗯，這樣我才能和主人說話，才能和主人手牽手散步，才能有一個身體讓主人……算了！\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Acid can be negated if you are in a boardable vehicle. Oh, me? Don't worry"
" about me. I'm acidproof♪\""
msgstr "\"如果你在可駕駛的載具裡，酸液可以被抵消。哦，我？別擔心我。我是防酸的♪\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid ""
"\"The lingering lightning after an electric shock reaches only one square "
"around! So if you wield a spear and a use a suitable martial art, you can "
"dodge it all! ...I have no idea what I just said.\""
msgstr "\"電擊後的殘留閃電隻影響周圍一格！所以如果你使用長矛和合適的武術，可以完全躲開！……我不知道我剛才在說什麼。\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Do you want to lay your head on my lap? It would make me comfortable, "
"too♪\""
msgstr "\"你想把頭枕在我的膝上嗎？那也會讓我很舒服♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"Please use me! Why don't you want to use me? Please use me! Use me!\""
msgstr "\"請使用我！你為什麼不想用我？請使用我！用我吧！\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"Master! Do you want to hold hands?\""
msgstr "\"主人！你想牽手嗎？\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"It's okay if master gets tied up! That way I can stay by your side as long"
" as I want... Ufufu...\""
msgstr "\"主人被綁起來也沒關係！那樣我就可以想待多久就待多久……唔呼呼……\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"No matter the weather, my heart beats on if I'm with my master♪\""
msgstr "\"無論天氣如何，只要和主人在一起，我的心就會跳動♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"Please use me as a shield in an emergency. I want to be useful and not be "
"like the other shoggoths.\""
msgstr "\"緊急情況下請把我當盾牌用。我想變得有用，不像其他修格斯那樣。\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"How many children do I want? As many as my master wishes... I will do my "
"best!\""
msgstr "\"我想要多少孩子？主人想要多少就有多少……我會努力的！\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid "\"Master's smell... it's intoxicating... haa, master...♪\""
msgstr "\"主人的氣味……令人陶醉……哈啊，主人……♪\""

#: .\speech.json .\talk_tags.json
msgid ""
"\"All my clothes and so on are made of my cells! It's okay if you touch me "
"more♪\""
msgstr "\"我所有的衣服等等都是由我的細胞構成的！你可以多碰我一點♪\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid ""
"\"Armored zombies are tough against random attacks, but if you're a good "
"trapper, you can penetrate and damage even the strongest armors! Destroying "
"knees with traps is the future!\""
msgstr "\"裝甲殭屍對隨機攻擊很堅韌，但如果你是個好陷阱師，甚至可以穿透並破壞最強的裝甲！用陷阱摧毀膝蓋才是未來！\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Master\""
msgstr "\"主人\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Master~\""
msgstr "\"主人~\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Mashterr\""
msgstr "\"主銀\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Master~~\""
msgstr "\"主人~~\""

#: .\speech.json
msgid "\"Master!\""
