#: .\talk_tags.json
msgid "Tekeli-li!"
msgstr "特克利-利！"

#: .\techniques.json
msgid "Coup de Grâce"
msgstr "致命一擊"

#: .\techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "You strike %s with an elegant coup de grâce"
msgstr "你以優雅的致命一擊擊中%s"

#: .\techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "<npcname> strikes %s in one elegant motion"
msgstr "<npcname>以優雅的動作擊中%s"

#: .\techniques.json
msgid "Desperate Counter"
msgstr "絕望反擊"

#: .\techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "You block %s's attack and shove them back. Back!"
msgstr "你格擋了%s的攻擊並將其推回。退後！"

#: .\techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "<npcname> struggles and forces %s back"
msgstr "<npcname>奮力掙扎，將%s逼退"

#: .\techniques.json
msgid "Spurn"
msgstr "輕蔑回擊"

#: .\techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "You whirl away and strike %s"
msgstr "你旋身避開並擊中%s"

#: .\techniques.json
msgid "<npcname> strikes with a malice that surprises you"
msgstr "<npcname>以出乎你意料的惡意發起攻擊"

#: .\techniques.json
msgid "Measured Strike"
msgstr "精準打擊"

#: .\techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "Your carefully placed strike sunders %s's guard"
msgstr "你精心佈置的一擊瓦解了%s的防禦"

#: .\techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "<npcname> lands a measured strike on %s"
msgstr "<npcname>對%s發動了一次精準打擊"

#: .\techniques.json
msgid "Measured Assault"
msgstr "精準猛攻"

#: .\techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "You assault %s with fury and dedication"
msgstr "你以狂怒與專注猛攻%s"

#: .\techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "<npcname> assaults %s with fury and dedication"
msgstr "<npcname>以狂怒與專注猛攻%s"

#: .\techniques.json
msgid "Anti-Molestation Technique No.15"
msgstr "防騷擾技巧第十五式"

#: .\techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "You dodge %s's groping lunge. Only master can touch that!"
msgstr "你躲開了%s的抓撲。只有主人才能碰那裡！"

#: .\techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "The %s tries to grab <npcname>, but they slip away!"
msgstr "%s試圖抓住<npcname>，但被他們溜走了！"

#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "leather cat tail (vibrator)"
msgid_plural "leather cat tail (vibrator)s"
msgstr[0] "皮革貓尾（震動器）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'leather cat tail (vibrator)'}
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid ""
"A shiny black cat tail made out of leather. Whenever you walk, it sways back"
" and forth. You can turn it on for extra enjoyment."
msgstr "一條閃亮的黑色皮革貓尾。每當你走動時，它會前後搖擺。你可以打開它以獲得額外樂趣。"

#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "furred cat tail (vibrator)"
msgid_plural "furred cat tail (vibrator)s"
msgstr[0] "毛皮貓尾（震動器）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'furred cat tail (vibrator)'}
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid ""
"A brown soft and furry cat tail. Whenever you walk, it sways back and forth."
" You can turn it on for extra enjoyment."
msgstr "一條棕色柔軟且毛茸茸的貓尾。每當你走動時，它會前後搖擺。你可以打開它以獲得額外樂趣。"

#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "blob cat tail"
msgid_plural "blob cat tails"
msgstr[0] "粘液貓尾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blob cat tail'}
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid ""
"A blob shaped like the tail of a cat that has been made docile. Whenever you"
" walk, it sways back and forth. Make sure to feed your new blob friend!"
msgstr "一個形狀像貓尾的粘液，已被馴服。每當你走動時，它會前後搖擺。記得餵養你的新粘液朋友！"

#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "human-sized carry bag"
msgid_plural "human-sized carry bags"
msgstr[0] "人形攜帶袋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'human-sized carry bag'}
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid ""
"A large bag that could fit a person inside. The zipper running across it "
"provides ventilation and you can open and close it from the inside. It can "
"be used as a sleeping bag, as well."
msgstr "一個可以裝下一個人的大袋子。貫穿袋子的拉鍊提供通風，你可以從內部打開和關閉它。它也可以用作睡袋。"

#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "maid cloak (off)"
msgid_plural "maid cloak (off)s"
msgstr[0] "女僕披風（關閉）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'maid cloak (off)'}.
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "You take a deep breath... And become invisible."
msgstr "你深吸一口氣……然後變得隱形。"

#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'maid cloak (off)'}.
#. ~ Use action need_charges_msg for {'str': 'white brim with veil', 'str_pl':
#. 'white brims with veils'}.
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "Not enough maid points!"
msgstr "女僕點數不足！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'maid cloak (off)'}
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid ""
"An elegant mantle to keep you warm when going outside. Use it to turn "
"invisible. Consumes maid points."
msgstr "一件優雅的斗篷，外出時為你保暖。使用它來隱身。消耗女僕點數。"

#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "maid cloak (on)"
msgid_plural "maid cloak (on)s"
msgstr[0] "女僕斗篷（開啟）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'maid cloak (on)'}.
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "You take a deep breath... And become visible again."
msgstr "你深吸一口氣……然後再次顯形。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'maid cloak (on)'}
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid ""
"An elegant mantle to keep you warm when going outside. Use it to turn "
"visible. It is currently on and consuming maid points."
msgstr "一件優雅的斗篷，外出時為你保暖。使用它來顯形。它當前已開啟並消耗女僕點數。"

#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "white brim with veil"
msgid_plural "white brims with veils"
msgstr[0] "帶面紗的白色帽簷"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'white brim with veil', 'str_pl': 'white brims
#. with veils'}.
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "You use the maid points and your vision expands."
msgstr "你使用女僕點數，視野隨之擴展。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'white brim with veil', 'str_pl': 'white brims
#. with veils'}
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid ""
"A regular maid's white brim with an elegant veil sewn into it, decorated "
"with silver frills. Although it covers your eyes and blocks your vision "
"quite harshly, you can use maid points to turn it on and gain otherwordly "
"sight."
msgstr "一頂普通女僕的白色帽簷，縫有優雅面紗，飾以銀色褶邊。儘管它遮住眼睛並嚴重阻礙視線，但你可以使用女僕點數開啟它，獲得超凡的視覺。"

#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid "white brim with veil (clairvoyant)"
msgid_plural "white brims with veils (clairvoyant)"
msgstr[0] "帶面紗的白色帽簷（透視）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'white brim with veil (clairvoyant)',
#. 'str_pl': 'white brims with veils (clairvoyant)'}.
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid ""
"The last bits of the maid points fizzle away and the veil turns back to "
"normal."
msgstr "女僕點數的最後一絲能量消散，面紗恢復正常。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'white brim with veil (clairvoyant)', 'str_pl':
#. 'white brims with veils (clairvoyant)'}
#: .\tool_armor.json
msgid ""
"A regular maid's white brim with an elegant veil sewn into it, decorated "
"with silver frills. It is currently see-through."
msgstr "一頂普通女僕的白色帽簷，縫有優雅面紗，飾以銀色褶邊。它當前是透明的。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "shoggoth heart"
msgid_plural "shoggoth meats"
msgstr[0] "修格斯心臟"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shoggoth heart', 'str_pl': 'shoggoth meats'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"The heart of a shoggoth. You could eat it to master the beast's morphogenic "
"prowess, or you could use it to 'master' the beast in another way."
msgstr "修格斯的心臟。你可以吃掉它以掌握這野獸的形態發生能力，或者用它以另一種方式“掌控”這野獸。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "flask (shoggoth)"
msgid_plural "flasks (shoggoth)"
msgstr[0] "燒瓶（修格斯）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'flask (shoggoth)', 'str_pl': 'flasks
#. (shoggoth)'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"The flask is threatening to shatter as the meat keeps growing. Use it again "
"to open it and relieve the pressure."
msgstr "燒瓶因肉塊持續生長而瀕臨破碎。再次使用以打開它，釋放壓力。"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'flask (shoggoth)', 'str_pl':
#. 'flasks (shoggoth)'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid "The piece of meat pulsates."
msgstr "肉塊在脈動。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flask (shoggoth)', 'str_pl': 'flasks
#. (shoggoth)'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"A glass flask containing a piece of meat that seems to be growing. "
"Occasionally the piece of meat pulsates."
msgstr "一個玻璃燒瓶，內含一塊似乎在生長的肉。偶爾肉塊會脈動。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "growing shoggoth maid"
msgid_plural "growing shoggoth maids"
msgstr[0] "成長中的修格斯女僕"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'growing shoggoth maid'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"The odd meat is released from its glass flask prison and begins to rapidly "
"and violently expand, extending numerous disjointed tentacles in every "
"direction. The tentacles intertwine with each other and transform into an "
"organism, resembling a beautiful woman, not quite like the horrible "
"nightmare creature it used to be. She suddenly speaks up: 'Finally, I am "
"able to meet you like this! Thank you for helping me, master!'"
msgstr ""
"奇異的肉塊從玻璃燒瓶的囚禁中釋放，開始迅速而猛烈地膨脹，向四面八方延伸出無數脫節的觸手。觸手相互交織，轉化成一個有機體，形似一位美麗的女子，不再像過去那可怕的噩夢生物。她突然開口：“終於，我能以這樣的方式見到您了！謝謝您幫助我，主人！”"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'growing shoggoth maid'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"The meat inside this flask glows with iridescent colors. It's lightly "
"shivering."
msgstr "燒瓶內的肉塊閃爍著虹彩光芒。它在輕微顫抖。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "small shoggoth maid"
msgid_plural "small shoggoth maids"
msgstr[0] "小型修格斯女僕"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'small shoggoth maid', 'str_pl': 'small
#. shoggoth maids'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"'I have made a complete recovery! I will serve you well, master! Now, please"
" put me on the ground.'"
msgstr "“我已完全恢復！我會好好服侍您，主人！現在，請把我放在地上。”"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'small shoggoth maid', 'str_pl':
#. 'small shoggoth maids'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"'Fufufu~ Are you worried? I am fine, your maid is fine! ... I guess. So, "
"please wait a bit longer... I'm sorry for making you concerned.'"
msgstr "“呼呼呼~ 您在擔心嗎？我沒事，您的女僕沒事！……我想是的。所以，請再稍等一會兒……抱歉讓您擔心了。”"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'small shoggoth maid', 'str_pl': 'small shoggoth
#. maids'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"'Ah... I think I went overboard and turned out like this. I need some time "
"to return to my former shape. Please warm me up in master's pockets! Don't "
"put me in a fridge! Absolutely not!'"
msgstr "“啊……我想我做得過火，變成這樣了。我需要一些時間恢復原形。請把我放在主人的口袋裡溫暖一下！不要把我放進冰箱！絕對不行！”"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "revitalized shoggoth maid"
msgid_plural "revitalized shoggoth maids"
msgstr[0] "恢復活力的修格斯女僕"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'revitalized shoggoth maid'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"'Sorry I kept you waiting, master! I will do my best to serve you and "
"support you to the best of my abilities!'"
msgstr "“抱歉讓您久等了，主人！我會盡我所能為您服務，全力支持您！”"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'revitalized shoggoth maid'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"'What's up? Why haven't you put me on the ground yet? Ah, you want me to "
"stay tiny for a little while longer? Ehh... I suppose it can't be helped.'"
msgstr "“怎麼了？為什麼還沒把我放在地上？啊，您想讓我再保持小巧一會兒？呃……我想這也沒辦法。”"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'master'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid "Master seemed worried about the state of the neighbors."
msgstr "主人似乎擔心鄰居的狀況。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "master doll"
msgid_plural "master dolls"
msgstr[0] "主人玩偶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'master doll'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"This is a doll in the shape of your beloved master. By keeping it in your "
"inventory, it slowly gathers maid power."
msgstr "這是一個您心愛主人形狀的玩偶。將其放在物品欄中，它會緩慢收集女僕能量。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "ceremony doll"
msgid_plural "ceremony dolls"
msgstr[0] "儀式玩偶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ceremony doll', 'str_pl': 'ceremony dolls'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"This is a doll in the shape of your beloved master, but with an additional "
"'special attachment.' By using it in a certain (rather embarassing) type of "
"private ritual, you can catalyze your powerful desires towards your beloved "
"master into a usable type of energy."
msgstr ""
"這是一個你心愛主人形狀的人偶，但附帶了一個‘特殊附件’。通過某種（相當令人尷尬的）私人儀式使用它，你可以將你對心愛主人的強烈慾望催化為一種可用的能量。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "master doll (vibrator) (off)"
msgid_plural "master doll (vibrator) (off)s"
msgstr[0] "主人玩偶（振動器）（關閉）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'master doll (vibrator) (off)'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"You can no longer suppress your feelings and began to intimately press "
"against your master's doll..."
msgstr "你再也無法抑制自己的感情，開始親密地緊貼著主人的玩偶……"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'master doll (vibrator) (off)'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"This is a doll in the shape of your beloved master, but with an additional "
"'special attachment.' By using it in a certain (rather embarassing) type of "
"private ritual, you can release an explosion of desire towards your beloved "
"master and transform it into a usable type of energy."
msgstr ""
"這是一個你心愛主人形狀的人偶，但附帶了一個‘特殊附件’。通過某種（相當令人尷尬的）私人儀式使用它，你可以釋放對心愛主人的慾望爆發，並將其轉化為一種可用的能量。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "master doll (vibrator) (on)"
msgid_plural "master doll (vibrator) (on)s"
msgstr[0] "主人玩偶（振動器）（開啟）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'master doll (vibrator) (on)'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"Finally, after your body tightens up and you reach your limit, you collapse "
"on the doll with a delighted and exhausted smile..."
msgstr "最終，在你的身體緊繃達到極限後，你帶著愉悅而疲憊的笑容癱倒在玩偶上……"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'master doll (vibrator) (on)'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"his is a doll in the shape of your beloved master, but with an additional "
"'special attachment.' By using it in a certain (rather embarassing) type of "
"private ritual, you can release an explosion of desire towards your beloved "
"master and transform it into a usable type of energy."
msgstr ""
"這是一個你心愛主人形狀的人偶，但附帶了一個‘特殊附件’。通過某種（相當令人尷尬的）私人儀式使用它，你可以釋放對心愛主人的慾望爆發，並將其轉化為一種可用的能量。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "scroll (summon little maid)"
msgid_plural "scroll (summon little maid)s"
msgstr[0] "卷軸（召喚小女僕）"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'scroll (summon little maid)'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"The sacrifical sugar melts at the apex of your casting and starts to spew "
"out white smoke. As the sweet smell spreads around, you notice a shadowy "
"figure about the size of a child standing in the magic circle. After the "
"smoke completely dissipates, a small maid stands in the place of the shadowy"
" figure, staring at you with curious eyes. 'Master?'"
msgstr ""
"獻祭的糖在你施法的頂點融化，開始噴出白煙。隨著甜味四散，你注意到一個孩童大小的黑影站在魔法陣中。煙霧完全消散後，一個小女僕取代了黑影的位置，用好奇的眼神盯著你。‘主人？’"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'scroll (summon little maid)'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"A set of scrolls and sacrifices used to summon a different kind of maid. "
"Pour the sacrificial sugar in the middle of the magic circle and cast the "
"correct spell."
msgstr "一套用於召喚另一種女僕的卷軸和祭品。將獻祭糖倒在魔法陣中央，並施放正確的咒語。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "little little maid"
msgid_plural "little little maids"
msgstr[0] "小小女僕"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'little little maid', 'str_pl': 'little little
#. maids'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"'Masteeer! Masteeeer!' The little maid taps your shoulder and points towards"
" the ground, as if she wants to get off your shoulder. Put her on the ground"
" when you're ready."
msgstr "‘主人！主人！’小女僕輕拍你的肩膀並指向地面，似乎想從你肩上下來。準備好時將她放到地上。"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'little little maid', 'str_pl':
#. 'little little maids'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"While standing still on the palm of your hand, she stares downwards and "
"mutters 'Master...' in a barely audible voice."
msgstr "她靜靜站在你的手掌上，低頭凝視，用幾乎聽不見的聲音低語‘主人……’。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'little little maid', 'str_pl': 'little little
#. maids'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid "An even smaller version of your little maid."
msgstr "你的小女僕的更加迷你版本。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "revitalized little maid"
msgid_plural "revitalized little maids"
msgstr[0] "恢復活力的小女僕"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'revitalized little maid'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"The little maid jumps down to the ground and turns around, lightly lifting "
"the hem of her skirt and giving you a bow. 'Master!' she says with a smile."
msgstr "小女僕跳落到地面，轉過身，輕輕提起裙襬向你鞠躬。‘主人！’她微笑著說道。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'revitalized little maid'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid "Your little maid seems to have made a complete recovery."
msgstr "你的小女僕似乎已經完全恢復了。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "scroll of recalling"
msgid_plural "scroll of recallings"
msgstr[0] "召回卷軸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'scroll of recalling'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"A mysterious scroll used to summon some kind of mystery meat and drinking "
"water. It can be used multiple times."
msgstr "一種用於召喚某種神秘肉塊和飲用水的神秘卷軸。可以多次使用。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "maid's cookware kit"
msgid_plural "maid's cookware kits"
msgstr[0] "女僕的廚具套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "maid's cookware kit"}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"A set of secret maid cookware. By powering it with maid energy, you can "
"create dishes filled with love."
msgstr "一套秘密的女僕廚具。通過注入女僕能量，你可以製作出充滿愛意的菜餚。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "little maid pet"
msgid_plural "little maid pets"
msgstr[0] "小女僕寵物"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'little maid pet'}
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"A summoned little maid. She looks and wanders around while holding onto the "
"hem of your clothes tightly. She's afraid of fighting."
msgstr "一隻被召喚的小女僕。她緊抓你的衣角四處張望和徘徊。她害怕戰鬥。"

#: .\tools.json
msgid "little maid pet (smoking meat)"
msgid_plural "little maid pet (smoking meat)"
msgstr[0] "小女僕寵物（熏製肉）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'little maid pet (smoking meat)', 'str_pl':
#. 'little maid pet (smoking meat)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'little maid pet (smoking human flesh)',
#. 'str_pl': 'little maid pet (smoking human flesh)'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid ""
"'Master! Master!' It seems like your little maid has finished smoking the "
"meat. It smells quite nice. Disassemble to recover the finished product."
msgstr "‘主人！主人！’你的小女僕似乎已經完成了燻肉。聞起來相當不錯。拆解以回收成品。"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'little maid pet (smoking meat)',
#. 'str_pl': 'little maid pet (smoking meat)'}.
#: .\tools.json
msgid "The little maid tastes the smoking meat and shakes her head a little."
