msgid "I have unleashed a disgusting monster..."
msgstr "我釋放了一個噁心的怪物……"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid " *pshhhttt* I'm reading you master, over."
msgstr "*滋滋聲* 收到您的信號，主人，完畢。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "What is it, master?"
msgstr "有什麼事嗎，主人？"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "I want to give you some commands for combat."
msgstr "我想給你下達一些戰鬥指令。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "I want to set some miscellaneous rules."
msgstr "我想設定一些雜項規則。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "I'd like to know a bit more about your abilities."
msgstr "我想多瞭解一下你的能力。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "There's something I want you to do."
msgstr "有件事想讓你去做。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "I just wanted to talk for a bit."
msgstr "我只是想聊一會兒天。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "It's time for your milking."
msgstr "該給你擠奶了。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "I'm going to go my own way for a while."
msgstr "我要自己行動一會兒。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Let's go."
msgstr "我們走吧。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid ""
" *tshk* Whatever you desire, master. Though perhaps we should meet up first?"
msgstr "*滋滋聲* 如您所願，主人。不過也許我們應該先會合？"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Is there something you need help with, master?"
msgstr "有什麼需要我幫忙的嗎，主人？"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Mind if we just chat for a bit about your history?"
msgstr "介意我們聊聊你的過去嗎？"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Let's just chitchat for a while, I could use some relaxation."
msgstr "我們隨便聊會兒天吧，我需要放鬆一下。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Can I do anything for you?"
msgstr "我能為您做些什麼嗎？"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "I don't want to ever be apart from you."
msgstr "我永遠都不想和你分開。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "I changed my mind, wanted to ask you something else."
msgstr "我改變主意了，想問你點別的。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Milking time♪ Please treat me well, master!"
msgstr "擠奶時間♪ 請好好對待我，主人！"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Later, then."
msgstr "那待會兒見。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Let's get to work."
msgstr "我們開始工作吧。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Ah...Ahn♪ Oh master, that feels so...good..."
msgstr "啊……嗯♪ 哦主人，這感覺……真舒服……"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "We're not done yet. I want your 'milk' too."
msgstr "我們還沒完呢。我還想要你的“奶水”。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "That's all for now."
msgstr "暫時就這些了。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid ""
"Th-there too? N-no, wait, I'm going to...! Master, please, I can't stop - "
"urgh, please, just let me rest...!"
msgstr "那、那裡也要？不、不行，等等，我要……！主人，求你了，我停不下來——呃啊，拜託，讓我休息一下……！"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid ""
"Oh master...♪ I feel the same way! But you know, there is a way we can be "
"together forever, no matter how cold or cruel this world is..."
msgstr "哦主人……♪ 我也有同感！但你知道嗎，有一種方法能讓我們永遠在一起，無論這個世界多麼寒冷或殘酷……"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Tell me more."
msgstr "詳細說說。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid ""
"Take my heart and eat it. Ah, don't worry♪ I won't die. My strength will "
"become our strength, and nobody will be able to separate us then!"
msgstr "拿走我的心臟並吃掉它。啊，別擔心♪ 我不會死的。我的力量將成為我們的力量，那時就沒人能將我們分開了！"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "This...let's do it. Now."
msgstr "這個……我們來做吧。現在。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "You know what? Never mind."
msgstr "你知道嗎？算了。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid ""
"For my beloved master, I would do anything! Oh, if you ever change your "
"mind, just put my heart back in the flask - I'll be back in no time!"
msgstr "為了我心愛的主人，我什麼都願意做！哦，如果你改變主意了，只要把我的心臟放回瓶子裡——我馬上就會回來的！"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "As you command, my master."
msgstr "遵命，我的主人。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Do you have orders for me?"
msgstr "您有命令要給我嗎？"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "How can I serve you?"
msgstr "我該如何為您效勞？"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Just say the word."
msgstr "儘管吩咐。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Can you teach me anything?"
msgstr "你能教我些什麼嗎？"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Let's trade items."
msgstr "我們來交換物品吧。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Let's trade items"
msgstr "我們來交換物品"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "I want you to use this item."
msgstr "我希望你使用這個物品。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Hold on to this item."
msgstr "保管好這個物品。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Guard this position."
msgstr "守衛這個位置。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Find a horse and mount up!"
msgstr "去找匹馬騎上！"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Get off your mount, please."
msgstr "請下馬。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Please go to this location."
msgstr "請前往這個地點。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Let's talk about your current activity."
msgstr "我們來談談你當前的活動。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "With my life, master!"
msgstr "以我的生命起誓，主人！"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "I need you to come with me."
msgstr "我需要你跟我來。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "See you around."
msgstr "回頭見。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "But master...you can just leave everything to me!"
msgstr "但是主人……您可以把一切都交給我！"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Come on, we're friends."
msgstr "得了吧，我們是朋友。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Forget it, let's get going."
msgstr "算了，我們出發吧。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid ""
"Are you sure?  This doesn't seem like a particularly safe place for small "
"talk…"
msgstr "你確定嗎？ 這地方似乎不太適合閒聊……"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "It's fine, we've got a moment."
msgstr "沒關係，我們還有點時間。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "You're right.  Forget I said anything, let's get moving."
msgstr "你說得對。忘了我剛才的話，我們繼續前進吧。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "My history? You mean before I served you? ...I'm sorry, but..."
msgstr "我的過去？你是指我侍奉你之前的事嗎？……抱歉，但是……"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Actually, never mind."
msgstr "算了，當我沒說。"

